          "story_body": "<p>Soie & Forme was born from a belief that the fabrics closest to your skin deserve the same quiet attention you bring to everything else. We source only the finest natural fibres — pure silk, linen, cotton — chosen for their hand-feel first and their beauty second.</p>",
